Class FeatureIntentModel<U,I,F>

  • java.lang.Object

        • es.uam.eps.ir.ranksys.diversity.intentaware.FeatureIntentModel<U,I,F>
  • Type Parameters:
    U - type of the users
    I - type of the items
    F - type of the features

    public class FeatureIntentModel<U,I,F>
extends IntentModel<U,I,F>
    Default feature-based intent-aware model. Features of the items in the user profiles are used as proxies for intents, and the probability of each is proportional to its occurrence in the profiles.
    Author:
    Sa√∫l Vargas (saul.vargas@uam.es), Pablo Castells (pablo.castells@uam.es)
